    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with various door dings, some fading on the clear coat, and minor scuffing on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows visible staining and wear on the driver's seat bolster, and some of the plastic trim pieces are loose. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it has high mileage and will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s an honest car that has been used regularly, offering a solid foundation for a buyer looking for utility over aesthetics.",
