    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a refined aesthetic, it offers a sophisticated balance of performance and long-term reliability. Every component has been thoroughly vetted to ensure the vehicle meets our rigorous standards for roadworthiness and presentation.",
      "price": 36800.0,
